FBIS3-11039 "drlat052_a_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-052 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba TV Cites Canadian Minister on Closer Latin Ties FL1703031394 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in Spanish 0100 GMT 17 Mar 94 FL1703031394 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Through its position against the economic blockade of Cuba, Canada is showing its intention to adopt a policy more independent of that of the United States and one of greater rapprochement to Latin America, said Canadian Foreign Minister Andre Ouellet today. The minister stressed the need to strengthen the ties between Canada and Latin America, a region in which, in his opinion, the OAS can play a decisive role.
